  "action_title": "Translocate (capture & release) wild primates from abundant population areas to non-inhabited environments",
  "key_messages": "Key Messages:\n\nOne replicated study in Belize\u00a0found that the majority of black howler monkeys survived for at least 10 months after translocation from abundant population areas to an uninhabited site, along with other interventions."
}

